    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《Code Alkonost》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款第一人称的氛围冒险游戏，斯拉夫传说在此复苏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入一个黑暗幻想世界，面对来自冥界的占有型幽灵。体验独特的艺术风格与从未在冒险游戏中呈现过的神秘故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/1206cc8458c8453ee8ab2d10af3c6b32.poster.avif?t=1755965263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/1206cc8458c8453ee8ab2d10af3c6b32.webm?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/1206cc8458c8453ee8ab2d10af3c6b32.mp4?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到黑暗幻想的世界</strong><br>双胞胎姐妹维拉（Vera）和米莱娜（Milena）前往斯拉夫神祇佩鲁恩（Perun）的雕像前献上礼物，希望神灵能赐予她们健康与在“人界”（<i>Jawia</i>）的平静生活。当维拉递上食物时，调皮的米莱娜躲了起来，最终引导维拉走向“禁地”的入口——这是一个被流放的死刑犯才会踏入的地方，人们相信那里游荡着恶魔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抵达禁忌森林后，维拉听到妹妹的尖叫声，毅然决定进入。森林大门随即关闭，夕阳早已西沉，逃离之路不复存在。<br><strong>欢迎进入黑暗童话……</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/269a3cea40d5d1b6620c126f3e41db91.poster.avif?t=1755965263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/269a3cea40d5d1b6620c126f3e41db91.webm?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/269a3cea40d5d1b6620c126f3e41db91.mp4?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>恐惧机制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作采用“恐惧效果”系统，能动态改变游戏的视听体验，营造压迫感与紧张氛围。恐惧会影响你的判断，让你必须跳出常规思维，才能生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/5747acb811b6d338dbd8bb1c478ecb40.poster.avif?t=1755965263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/5747acb811b6d338dbd8bb1c478ecb40.webm?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/5747acb811b6d338dbd8bb1c478ecb40.mp4?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越 Jawia 与 Nawia</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏剧情深受斯拉夫神话和黑暗幻想文学的影响。玩家将在“人界”（Jawia）与“冥界”（Nawia）之间穿梭，遇见传说中的野兽，完成神灵的试炼，解开神秘谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/6ae860d377ace32d385af6c7778bb6ce.poster.avif?t=1755965263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/6ae860d377ace32d385af6c7778bb6ce.webm?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/6ae860d377ace32d385af6c7778bb6ce.mp4?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>谜题与成长</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将学习如何运用**拉达之星（Lada Star）**来抵御敌人。通过解谜、互动和探索动态环境，逐步深入这个扭曲世界的各个角落，解锁隐藏的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/38937ab08776bacab2b5ba28b5d356f4.poster.avif?t=1755965263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/38937ab08776bacab2b5ba28b5d356f4.webm?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/38937ab08776bacab2b5ba28b5d356f4.mp4?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一段心理成长的旅程</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作讲述了一位少女的心灵成长之路。她踏上了自我探索的旅程，发现自己独特的能力与命运。在不断成长的过程中，她勇敢面对心魔，并抗拒那些试图控制她身体与灵魂的黑暗力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/d22bf19fa5f856a7c209b80ac9d10c05.poster.avif?t=1755965263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/d22bf19fa5f856a7c209b80ac9d10c05.webm?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062030/extras/d22bf19fa5f856a7c209b80ac9d10c05.mp4?t=1755965263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真实民族音乐</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏原声以斯拉夫民俗音乐为基础，加入现代编曲与节奏变化。在紧张时刻音乐将加快，增强玩家的危机感。阴森的音效与诡异旋律，将带你深入黑森林与荒废的古堡，感受深沉压迫的氛围。</p>",
